  <div><span>诽</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［fěi］<br>［《廣韻》甫微切，平微，非。］<br>［《廣韻》方味切，去未，非。］<br>［《集韻》府尾切，上尾，非。］<br>“非2”的被通假字。“诽1”的繁体字。<br>(1)从旁指责过失。<br>(2)毁谤。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诽</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【酉集上】【言字部】　誹； 康熙笔画：15； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/1188.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页1188第18</span></a><br>【唐韻】【正韻】敷尾切【集韻】【韻會】妃尾切，?音斐。【說文】謗也。【博雅】䛼也。【史記·高祖紀】誹謗者族。【莊子·刻意篇】高論怨誹。【戰國策】國必有誹譽，忠臣令誹在己，譽在上。　又【集韻】或省作非。【前漢·鼂錯傳】非謗不治。【師古註】非讀曰誹。　又【集韻】府尾切，非上聲。義同。　又【集韻】【韻會】匪微切【正韻】芳微切。?與非通。【類篇】謗言也。【增韻】非議也。【史記·平準書】張湯奏顏異當九卿，見令不便，不入言而腹誹。【前漢·食貨志】作腹非。【註】口不言，心非之也。又【廣韻】方味切【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】方未切，?非去聲。義同。【史記·文帝紀】誹謗之木。【索隱】誹，音非，亦音沸。尸子云：堯立誹謗之木。韋昭云：慮政有缺失，使書于木，後代遂因以爲飾。今宮牆橋樑頭四柱木是也。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诽</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>诽</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>暂无。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">slander<br>Basic explanation of words<br>slander<br>(slander)<br>fěi<br>Fabricate facts and speak ill of others: slander. Slander chapter. Belly slander.<br>slander<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［fěi］<br>[\"Guangyun\" is slightly cut, flat and non-existent. ]<br>[\"Guangyun\" Fang Wei is cut, go is not, no. ]<br>[\"Ji Yun\" Fu tail cut, upper tail, non. ]<br>\"Non-2\" was passed falsely. Traditional Chinese characters for \"Sorrow 1\".<br>(1) Accuse of negligence from the side.<br>(2) Defamation.<br>slander<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[You Ji 1] [Words Department] 　 slander; Kangxi strokes: 15; page number: page 1188 page 18<br>[Tang Yun] [Zheng Yun] Putting the tail cut [Ji Yun] [Rhyme meeting] Concubine tail cutting,? Yin Fei. [Said the text] slander also. [Bo Ya] Ni Ye. [Historical Records · Gao Zu Ji] The family of slanderers. [Zhuangzi: Deliberate Articles] Highly discuss grievances and slanders. [Warring States Policy] The country must have slander, and the loyal ministers order to slander themselves, and to honor them.　[Jiyun] or province is wrong. 【The wrong biography of the former Han·鼂】It was not cured for slander. [Shigu Note] Non-reading is slanderous.　[Jiyun] Futail cut, not on sound. The same meaning.　 [Ji Yun] [Yun Hui] Bandit micro-cut [Zheng Yun] Fang micro-cut. ? And non-communication. [Classes] slander words. [Zeng Yun] criticism also. [Historical Records·Leveling Book] Zhang Tang played Yan Yi as Jiuqing, which is inconvenient and slander without words. 【Previous Han·Shihuo Zhi】have feuds. [Note] The words are not spoken, but the heart is wrong. Also [Guangyun] Fang Weiqie [Jiyun] [Yunhui] [Zhengyun] Fang is not cut, not Qusheng. The same meaning. 【Historical Records · Wen Di Ji】The wood of slander. [Suoyin] slander, the sound is not, but the sound is boiling. Shi Ziyun: Yao Li is the wood of slander. Wei Zhaoyun: Considering the lack of politics, so that the book Yumu, the future generations will be decorated for it. The four-pillar wood at the head of the Imamiya wall bridge is also.<br>slander<br>Source glyph<br>slander<br>Name meaning<br>Nothing.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274098112553.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274098112553.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148274098112553.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">会意字。从言(i),篆书形体像张口伸舌说话,表示用语言来指责;从非,非有不合、不对之义,表示诽是指责不对的言<br>行;非(fi)兼表声。誹简化为诽。本义是用语言来指责过失。<br>后用于贬义,指无中生有,说别人坏话,毁坏别人的名誉。<br>说别人的坏话:~谤|腹~。<br>~谤 腹~ 腹~心谤<br>诽<br>fěi<br>跳|離誰诽</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">Зная слово.<br>Congyan (i), печать печати подобна открытому рту и языку для разговора, что означает использование языка для обвинения; Congfei, несоответствие, неправильное значение, означает, что клевета - это обвинение в неправильных словах и действиях; non (fi) тоже голос.<br>Клевета сводится к клевете.<br>Первоначальный смысл - использовать язык для обвинения в халатности.<br>Позже 